Global Oxidative Stress Assay Market key Developments:

• Aytu Bioscience, Inc announced the availability of MiOXSYS, a first-in-class seminal oxidative stress test specifically developed for the evaluation of male infertility in South Africa, in September 2019. This is the first in vitro diagnostic test that can detect oxidative stress in the seminal fluid. The MiOXSYS method is also a great way to monitor how well an antioxidant treatment is working.
